{
  "id": "adv_main_02_02_01",
  "title": "東京編1章6話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "私達三人を……TRINITYAiLEを\n星見プロダクションに、移籍させて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could you please allow… the three of us from TRINITYAiLE…\nto sign up with Hoshimi Productions?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.166666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "い、移籍って……\n一体、何があったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sign up?\nWhat in the world happened?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.100000000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "それは……ええっとですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… uhh‚ it’s complicated…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "すみません……正直、私達も\nまだ整理出来てないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry… To be honest‚ we still\nhaven’t even sorted out the details.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.200000000000003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "せやから、順を追って説明します\n昨日の夜なんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So we’ll try to explain everything in order.\nStarting with last night…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――昨日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Yesterday",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.900000000000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 28.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 28.8
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tri-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 28.933333333333337
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "今日のレッスンも盛り沢山やったなあ\nそれに、ダンスの難易度上がったんちゃう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today's lesson was a lot of fun!\nAnd is it just me‚ or did the difficulty of the steps increase?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 36.66666657387673
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね。でもそれだけ、どんどん上手になってて\n新しいことを頑張ってるってこと……だよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. But I guess that just means we’re getting better and better\nand working hard at learning new things. Right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.56666657387675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 44.46666657387677
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。もし「楽」とか「簡単」って感じている\nようなら、それは停滞しているって証拠だから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. If this felt too “fun” or “easy‚”\nthat would be proof that we’re stagnating.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.39999990721008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "ほんならうちら、グランプリの前より\n成長してるってことやな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then that means we’ve improved a lot\nsince before the Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.5246818481558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 55.99134851482247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "その実感は、十分に感じてる\nもちろん、まだまだ足りないけれどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I feel more than enough evidence of that.\nThough‚ we still have a long way to go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.42468184815582,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 60.95801518148917
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "成長と言えば……最近は瑠依ちゃんも\n前より社長と仲良く話せるようになったもんな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of improving‚ Rui-chan… you and the president\nhave gotten a lot friendlier with each other lately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.82468184815579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 68.69134851482247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "な、仲良くって\n別に、そういうつもりじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "F-friendly?\nThat wasn’t my intention.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.69134851482247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 72.89134851482247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、NEXT VENUSグランプリの時\nほんの少し認めてくれたのが、嬉しかったから？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When he accepted you a little as his daughter\nat the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix‚ that made you happy‚ didn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.72468184815581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 78.85801518148914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "もう……やめてよ\nそれも……少しはあるかもしれない、けど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Jeez… cut it out.\nWell… I guess that did make me a little happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.65801518148912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 84.65801518148912
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "グランプリで負けて、もっと上を目指さないとって\n思った時……頼れるのは社長だったから……それだけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But when we lost the Grand Prix‚ and I realized I had to aim higher‚\nthe only one I could depend on was him… that’s all there is to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.09134851482246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 92.99650111569929
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "私達トリエルのためにも、関係は改めたい\nそう思ってるだけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For TRINITYAiLE’s sake‚ as well as mine‚ I want to redefine our relationship.\nThat’s it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.82983444903265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 98.76316778236598
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ\nせやったら、そういうことにしておきましょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe.\nOkay‚ I’ll take your word for it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.79650111569924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 102.89650111569924
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、社長、どうしたんだろうね\n急に話があるって……なんのことだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I wonder what’s going on with the president?\nHe said he wanted to speak with us urgently… What could it be?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.56316778236594,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5833.3333333332575,
          "startTime": 112.3965011156992
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6333.3333333332575,
          "startTime": 112.8965011156992
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 111.79650111569924
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 111.79650111569924
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "失礼します\nトリエルの三人、揃いました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me.\nAll of us from TRINITYAiLE are here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.06316778236592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 116.76316778236593
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　姫野さんも同席ですか？\n珍しいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Himeno-san‚ you’re here‚ too?\nThat’s unusual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.99650111569927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ええ。私も、今し方呼び出されて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I was called to be here just now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.06316778236594,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3286.258459091485,
          "startTime": 125.34942624145742
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "揃ったようだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looks like everyone’s here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.34942624145712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 125.34942624145742
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "急な呼び出しですまない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry to call this meeting out of the blue.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.3160929081238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "いえ。そういえば今日\nレッスン中にコーチから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s okay. Now that you mention it‚\nduring our lesson today‚ the coach—",
        "id": ""
      },
